high_descs: Turn around, go to the sink
Pick up the knife in front of the sink
Turn around, go forward, turn left to the table
Slice the potato on the table
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the table
Pick up a potato slice from the table
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the sink
Put the potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cool a potato slice

high_descs: Turn right and head to the sink
Pick up the knife in front of the sink
Turn right then head to the round table
Slice the potato on the round table
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open and put in the knife then close it
Turn right then head to the round table
Pick up a slice of potato
Turn left head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the slice potato
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the slice potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled slice potato in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and move to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter in front of the sink.
Turn around and carry the knife to the round table.
Use the knife to slice the potato on the table.
Turn left, and after a couple steps head right to the fridge
Place the knife in the fridge on the top shelf next to the tomato.
Turn right and return to the sliced potato on the table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn left to carry the potato slice to the fridge.
Place the potato slice on the shelf next to the knife in the fridge, close the door, and then open the door to remove it after a few seconds.
Carry the potato slice to the kitchen sink.
Place the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cold potato in the sink.
